statements: SELECT * FROM website_traffic_analysis WHERE website_id = 1;
SELECT website_id, page_views FROM website_traffic_analysis WHERE date_visited = '2022-01-01';
SELECT conversion_rate, traffic_source FROM website_traffic_analysis WHERE website_id > 5;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_analysis ORDER BY page_views DESC;
SELECT website_id, date_visited, page_views FROM website_traffic_analysis WHERE conversion_rate >= 0.5;
SELECT website_id, page_views, conversion_rate, traffic_source, date_visited FROM website_traffic_analysis WHERE conversion_rate >= 0.5 ORDER BY date_visited DESC, page_views ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT page_views, AVG(conversion_rate) AS average_conversion_rate FROM website_traffic_analysis GROUP BY page_views HAVING page_views > 100 ORDER BY average_conversion_rate DESC
SELECT traffic_source, COUNT(*) AS total_visits FROM website_traffic_analysis WHERE date_visited BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31' GROUP BY traffic_source ORDER BY total_visits DESC
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_analysis WHERE website_id IN (1, 3, 5) AND traffic_source = 'Google' ORDER BY date_visited ASC, page_views DESC

SELECT website_id, page_views, conversion_rate, date_visited FROM website_traffic_analysis WHERE date_visited = '2022-03-15' AND (conversion_rate < 0.3 OR traffic_source = 'Direct') ORDER BY website_id ASC
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE visitor_id = 12345;

SELECT id, conversion_rate, conversion_timestamp FROM conversion_rates ORDER BY conversion_timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT page_url, COUNT(visitor_id) AS visitor_count FROM website_traffic GROUP BY page_url HAVING visitor_count > 100
SELECT AVG(conversion_rate) AS avg_conversion_rate, page_url FROM conversion_rates GROUP BY page_url ORDER BY avg_conversion_rate DESC
